The course deals with the critical reading and generalisation of the modern scientific literature in the various sport disciplines. Students acquire the knowledge and experience to implement the results of modern scientific literature in the daily work of the coach.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to give a profound knowledge how to apply results from the research in the field of sport science to the practical coaching.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student: 1) is familiar with the scientific literature of different sports; 2) is able to critically read, evaluate, and make generalizations from different sports scientific publications; 3) knows how to apply results from the research of sport science into the practical work of the coach.
